<#cdcfbbfa464a23605007d2c667085b41> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/srv/resources/distributions/d6a25f1b-90ae-4aba-a851-64ed253a6d0c>;
