<#73d0869b8432e5234747c83855818563> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/srv/resources/distributions/a6405f51-6a93-423b-b68d-854826bfad06>;
